<TEXT>
<P>
I was shocked and horrified when I read the news accounts about the two captive 
killer whales (Kandu and Corky) who were forced to compete against each other 
in the San Diego Sea World park in order to titillate the watching audiences. I 
realize that Kandu broke her jaw after charging into the other whale -- but Sea 
