<P>
'Mahagonny' Opera -- In Saturday's Calendar, two inadvertently transposed lines 
altered quotes about director Jonathan Miller by singers Marvellee Cariaga and 
Louis Lebherz. Cariaga said, "He's infectious" and admires him . . . "for 
letting us bring in our own ideas." Lebherz said, "Jonathan helped me out with 
the verbal image. He talked about the wooden cob-webbed cog that began to turn 
in my brain and how everything developed from that." 
